data.text:
-> WB Police Constable 2024 Application Correction Window has been activated

-> Candidates can edit and rectify their application form by providing details of serial number, mobile number, and date of birth.

-> A total of 11749 vacancies have been announced.

-> Candidates had applied from 7th March 2024 to 5th April 2024.

> The WB Police Constable selection process includes a Written Test, PMT, PET, and Interview.

-> Candidates appointed to this post will be entitled to a pay scale of Rs. 22,700 to Rs. 58,500.
